Class AbstractStreet

java.lang.Object
com.company.AbstractStreet
All Implemented Interfaces:
Lengthed, Street
Direct Known Subclasses:
ArrayListStreet, LDLinkedListStreet, LinkedListStreet, OldStreet
public abstract class AbstractStreet extends Object implements Street
AbstractStreet is the abstract class that contains and manages all the common properties of differently implemented streets.
